    • Method Detail

      • getInternal

        T getInternal()
        get the value in a representation used internally to the class. the internal format keeps the value as positive so sign is separately managed
        Returns:
        the internal representation of the value

      • getUnderlying

        T getUnderlying()
        get the value in a representation used generally. the underlying format allows for zero and negative values as this is the export from the Value wrapper
        Returns:
        the generalized representation of the value
